data.name: infoLabel.Text
data.value:
The game Othello is played on an 8x8 board where the goal is to controll the most spaces you can with your color.
The user who is using the black coin goes firsts by picking a space on the board to turn to his. Next it is the user who is using whites turn to select a space.
You are able to take over the opponents space by having two pieces surrounding one of theirs in a straight line.
